summary:
Day 16 of #Drawlloween2018 "Party At Doom Lagoon". I decided to draw 
another Bloodborne boss; this time it's the Orphan of Kos....
caption:
Day 16 of #Drawlloween2018 “Party At Doom Lagoon”. I decided to draw another Bloodborne boss; this time it’s the Orphan of Kos. I went with him because you can fight him in the water of that area…and since it’s a stupid hard boss, I consider it “DOOM” Lagoon…Shaddap. I’m going with this.

Check out my Halloween Collab.
